==English==
{{wp}}
{{commonscat}}

===Etymology===
From {{bor|en|ru|Узбекистан}}, itself from {{der|en|fa-cls|اُزْبَکِسْتَان}}. Ultimately {{unc|en|nocap=1}}; possibly from {{der|en|trk|-}} {{m|tr|uz||genuine}} + {{der|en|sog|ts=bek|t=master}} (for the second element, see [[Turkish]] {{m|tr|bey}}). The suffix is known to be from {{der|en|fa-cls|ـِستان|tr=istān||place of}}. {{surf|en|Uzbek|-i-|-stan}}.

